{"tid":1156914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明報 : 陳恒鑌 葛珮帆受傷 中藥界送上鎮痛貼","createTime":"2019-05-16T02:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T02:35:31.000Z","uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"107a1a5cfe5002bf05b9ac349fd7be953bcb944d","tid":1156914,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:06:20.000Z","msg":"明報 (2019/05/16)<br />\n上星期六修訂《逃犯條例》法案委員會民主派同建制派議員爆發衝突，兩營議員都有受傷。民建聯陳恒鑌（Ben）同葛珮帆（EQ）分別整親膊頭同頸背，EQ噚日話<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">𠵱家仲係好痛，坐得耐就要食止痛藥</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，要睇中醫做針灸。至於當日要保安包紮三角巾、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">事後醫生證實係肌肉繃緊同軟組織受壓</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘅阿Ben，就仲睇緊跌打。有中藥界朋友就送上鎮痛貼，兩人話估唔到做議員要捱得打，仲要識得打「木人巷」先入到去開會喎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://premium.mingpao.com/protected/Image/20190516/_16gk401.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpremium.mingpao.com%2Fprotected%2FImage%2F20190516%2F_16gk401.jpg&h=8dd2230e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abf769daaa2a9bfd368bbdb9b30c44ad34d0ba35","tid":1156914,"uid":61882,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:32:33.000Z","msg":"幾時到殯儀界送全家破地獄套餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a78a5c060c4d502aac4ed354e94dd117c76c96","tid":1156914,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:35:31.000Z","msg":"香港市民見到建制派議員做啲實事都一樣頭痛作嘔"}]}